{"tid":1602127,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"dgx致中學生集會公開信 (核實用)","createTime":"2019-09-29T10:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T16:33:14.000Z","uid":105976,"like":63,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cdf125c03444cd2ee514a1ac023b581d357ff124","tid":1602127,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T10:02:14.000Z","msg":"致中學生集會公開信:<br />\n<br />\n各位好, 我是thomas dgx, <br />\n<br />\n我並不比你們年長很多。<br />\n我以前都算是一個普通學生， <br />\n但我中學時也試過為了不公義的事罵老師，大學畢業之後為了夢想放棄了專業行業。<br />\n我並非鼓勵你們反叛， 而是要忠於自己的信念， 只有你才知自己的目標。<br />\n<br />\n很多人只看表面及只顧利益而指摘我們， 因為他們不明白有東西比金錢及個人利益重要。<br />\n<br />\n這次會是長期抗爭，願大家勇氣智慧永不滅， 獨立思考，各施所長。<br />\n<br />\n今日很榮幸可以同這麼多人一起為身邊人、 為自己、為其他人，爭取建立一個更自由、更幸福的香港。<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港 <br />\n<br />\nThomas dgx"},{"pid":"f0307be07f951020e61991cda5835ed5b9a0f419","tid":1602127,"uid":254456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T10:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67eb4ca023f3136e5e3aff9f70cc80f60da291a4","tid":1602127,"uid":124252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T10:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0bfe16cbae1f2fba80d65422a40ebe7685fd42","tid":1602127,"uid":241000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e832a95f0e381ffdb2da05ecdf57567500443d","tid":1602127,"uid":10189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T10:14:54.000Z","msg":"大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369a7ee93023542769aff69395f7233f25025589","tid":1602127,"uid":146724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T10:18:24.000Z","msg":"好鼓舞<br />\n